CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Corporacion America Airports SA acquires, develops and operates airport concessions. Its operating segments are geographically divided into Argentina, Italy, Brazil, Uruguay, Ecuador, Armenia and Peru. The company generates a majority of its revenue from the Argentina segment. The firm's revenue is categorized in Aeronautical Revenue, Non-Aeronautical Revenue, Commercial Revenue, Construction Service Revenue, and Other Revenue.
